02:E878 B68004          	  1614: tain2:      ldaa tp                     ; acca from tape
02:E87B 46              	  1615:             rora                        ; data bit in carry
02:E87C 39              	  1616:             rts
02:E87D B68009          	  1617: ttyin2:     ldaa tty                    ; acca from acia
02:E880 39              	  1618:             rts
02:E881 B78009          	  1619: ttyo2:      staa tty                    ; send acca to acia
02:E884 39              	  1620:             rts
